sufficient interest. After all, Sherlock Holmes Society has been going for some

15:21.600 --> 15:33.380
time, and there's now no longer any possibility of more Sherlock Holmes stories.
It doesn't seem to worry them at all. And with what we already have of Middle

15:33.380 --> 15:44.840
-earth, we can keep going for a considerable number of years. And, of course, we
mustn't forget that the professor did a lot of pure academic linguistic

15:44.840 --> 15:55.440
